{"title":"机床厂的歌","authors":["梁上泉"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":10,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"机床厂的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁上泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬头见喜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论你走到哪里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都能抬头见喜："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜报贴满了墙壁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"超过长城万里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里长城贴不下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千层万层重叠起；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重叠起，红透底。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国就在一片红光里！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人的手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要圆就圆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要方就方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要短就短，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要长就长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凭着机械工人的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驯服铁和钢；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凭着机械工人的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把世界变个样！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一朵花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蚂蚁啃骨头——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人志气大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"制成发电机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一千五百瓩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当场报喜讯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢迎党委书记来讲话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家看书记，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书记看大家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一同苦战了几昼夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼里的血丝密麻麻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锣鼓声中他没开口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手给它插了一朵花；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都说在打扮新姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天就出嫁……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女辅助工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推着小车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿着铁铲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙碌在车间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地板打扫得发亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机床也显得好看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车刀下铁屑飞溅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她都当作花瓣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细心地扫积起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不让它抛撒一片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送回炉里熔炼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她眉毛笑得最弯："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“在这铁水里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也有我的一滴汗！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}